{"tid":2182782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[831太子] 戇鳩黑警：記者你唔著制服嘅","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T19:27:02.000Z","uid":301666,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca16ce5d7b06474cbb304f0e618118a664b90f0","tid":2182782,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"警方在始創中心門外截停一男兩女，蘋果記者在拍攝期間，被一名態度惡劣的警員以警棍指喝，質疑其記者身份。<br />\n<br />\n另一名警員乘勢追問：「你唔帶制服嘅？」記者反駁：「記者唔係紀律部隊，係無制服㗎！」該名警員其後再無回應。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果記者接著向讀者解釋，記者並沒有所謂制服，反光背心只為方便識別，並非一定需要穿著，而每位記者都會配戴記者證，以作核實身份。<br />\n<br />\n記者話音剛落，該批警員隨即「報復式」向記者方向推進，又用強光電筒照向記者，妨礙拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159407797312448&amp;id=105259197447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10159407797312448%26id%3D105259197447&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr0w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=876ebb86\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10159407797312448&amp;id=105259197447</a>"},{"pid":"5f9083cc60d3925a2842566090bfa3a2ab4a0e25","tid":2182782,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"link入面有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eabb0f903c83fd139969fe7b0056b681d88c4e3","tid":2182782,"uid":333470,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"似得班狗連狗牌都唔敢show咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d11024969ed87d9ce29b6313193d9af80cfe8c","tid":2182782,"uid":301666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2eabb0f903c83fd139969fe7b0056b681d88c4e3","tid":2182782,"uid":333470,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"似得班狗連狗牌都唔敢show咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hk